descript.abstract: This layer contains boundary polygons depicting the State of Georgia's Voter Precinct Districts as adopted by the Georgia General Assembly in June 2006. This data contains all updates submitted by the counties to the Georgia Reapportionment Services Office. The geographic extent of this layer is the state of Georgia.
descript.purpose: Used to delineate voter precinct districts for the Georgia General Assembly
